  description="Words removed from Scrabble dictionaries, slang that divides players, and how dictionary committees decide what stays. The politics of word validity. Free."
  keywords="controversial scrabble words, banned scrabble words, removed scrabble words, offensive words scrabble, scrabble dictionary debate, scrabble slang words, NASPA word list changes"
